      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>Correspondence and manuscripts of Drury, relating to his campaign for official
            world-wide adoption of the metric system of weights and measures. The collection also
            contains a considerable quantity of clippings.</p>
         <p/>
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement encodinganalog="351">
